The paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques in computer systems, which is a topic that falls under several CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on the use of machine learning systems and their potential. The paper also discusses security as a requirement, which suggests cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as another likely category. The paper also touches on system complexity and its impact on machine learning systems, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper discusses reproducibility as a key requirement, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
